&lt;p>最后将文档保存到 Application 目录，命名为“Neovide”。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>用 SuperDuper! 配合迁移助理加速 Mac 的迁移</title><link>http://0x3f.org/posts/speed-up-mac-migration-with-superduper-and-migration-assistant/</link><pubDate>Sat, 05 Aug 2023 22:29:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://0x3f.org/posts/speed-up-mac-migration-with-superduper-and-migration-assistant/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xbot/image-hosting/master/blog/2023-08-05-22-44-49-IMG_0191.jpeg" alt="2023-08-05-22-44-49-IMG_0191">&lt;/p>
